description:
Hideouts are in-game real estate for your characters in Psyker. These hideouts allow you to store your gear, display it, and you are able to interact with the environment in third person.
The themes of the hideouts reflect the different environments in the game world.
The themes in the collection are Sewer, Street Bar, Robotics Lab, and Corporate Penthouse.
Hideouts have visual variations based on the rarity of the hideout. There will be different items and cosmetic environments in each type of hideout.
Hideouts also have vault capacities. Vault system is used to store NFT items out of your inventory and in your hideout. This system is used to be able to showcase your items in game, store them, and build equity by including those items with your hideout listing on the marketplace.
For example: if you have an Epic Sewer with 50 vault capacity, you can list that hideout on a marketplace with up to 50 items included; increasing its potential market value.
name: Psyker - Hideouts
